# Smart Agriculture — 墒情 Agent QA 规则

> 架构版本：LLM + Function Calling 5 节点（2026-04-27 迁移）。IntentSlot / ExecutionGate / RuleEngine / Template 管线已删除。

Follow this rule when the task involves testing, regression, or business review of the soil-moisture Agent. Read the full skill at `.claude/skills/soil-moisture-qa/SKILL.md`.

## 资产速查

| 资产 | 路径 |
|------|------|
| **正式 Case 主库（唯一入口）** | `testdata/agent/soil-moisture/case-library.md` |
| Agent 能力方案 | `apps/agent/plans/1/1.plan.md` |
| 回答类型与业务边界 | `apps/agent/plans/1/2.answer-types-business.md` |

## 架构约束速查

**4 Tools：** `query_soil_summary` / `query_soil_ranking` / `query_soil_detail` / `diagnose_empty_result`

**5 answer_types：** `soil_summary_answer` / `soil_ranking_answer` / `soil_detail_answer` / `guidance_answer` / `fallback_answer`

**P0 红线：** 业务问题未调用 Tool 直接回答 → 强制截停为 `fallback_answer`（fallback_reason=tool_missing）

